posts.subject: Where has everyone gone?
posts.body: With 8chan being dead, and 8kun dead on arrival (there's no /tech/ in the lokinet version?), where has everyone moved to? I take it some specific boards have moved to specific bunkers, but I can't really find one for /tech/.
